                </div>
                <div type="section" xml:id="TITLE">
                    <head type="section">Title</head>
                    <p>Untitled in draft. When a revised version was published in the literary annual, 
                        <ref type="note" subtype="bibliographical" target="friendships_offering_note.php"><hi rend="italic">Friendship&#x02BC;s Offering</hi></ref> 
                        (see <ref type="internal" target="#COMPPUB">Composition and Publication</ref>), 
                        the poem first exhibited its title, &#x201C;Saltzburg&#x201D;; however, this title must have been determined by that of the steel engraving, 
                        which the poem was commissioned to accompany.</p>
                </div>
                <div type="section" xml:id="GENRE">
                    <head type="section">Genre</head>
                    <p>Ekphrastic and topographical poem.</p>
                </div>
                <div type="section" xml:id="MAJORMS">
                    <head type="section">Manuscripts</head>
                    <p>Draft contained in <ref type="apparatus" subtype="manuscript" target="msviii_apparatus.php">MS VIII</ref> 
                        (see <ref type="apparatus" subtype="manuscript" target="msviii_apparatus#LISTB2.php">Contents, list <hi rend="italic">b</hi>.2</ref>).</p>
                    <p>Facsimiles by permission of <title type="archive" corresp="#BEINECKERUSKINCOLLECTION">John Ruskin Collection</title>, General Collection, <orgName corresp="#BEINECKE">Beinecke Rare Book and Manuscript Library</orgName>, <orgName corresp="#YALE">Yale University</orgName>. Transcriptions of texts and commentary &#x00A9; <persName corresp="#DCH">David C. Hanson</persName>.</p>
                </div>
                <div type="section" xml:id="DATE">
                    <head type="section">Date</head>
                    <p>Composed probably between May and July 1834, in time for submission deadline in August.</p>
                </div>
                <div type="section" xml:id="COMPPUB">
                    <head type="section">Composition &#x0026; Publication</head>
                    <p>Published in <ref type="bibliography" target="bibliography.php#FRIENDSHIPSOFFERING1835"><hi rend="italic">Friendship&#x02BC;s Offering; and Winter&#x02BC;s Wreath . . . for MDCCCXXXV</hi></ref>, 317&#x2013;19).</p>
                </div>
